          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em><strong>1. The reviews.</strong></em><br/>Over 16,000 verified customer reviews. The highest rated portable hot tub brand in the UK on Trustpilot. </p><p><em><strong>2. The range.</strong></em><br/>Four product lines - Inflatable, foam, drop-stitch, and frame  covering every budget and every kind of garden. Whatever you need a hot tub to be, we make one.</p><p><em><strong>3. Set up in an afternoon.</strong></em><br/>No tools, no contractor, no patio required. Customers are soaking the same day their delivery arrives.</p><p><em><strong>4. Built for British weather.</strong></em><br/>Wave Spas are designed to live outside, year-round. Insulated for winter and tested in conditions that don't usually make the brochure.</p><p><em><strong>5. A decade of doing this.</strong></em><br/>We've been making portable hot tubs for nearly ten years. The product has been refined across that whole time, by the people who actually use it. The reviews are what's left when you do that for long enough.</p>",
